\begin_layout Chapter
Getting Started
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
This document provides general instructions for using the Java-based Graphical
 User Interface (GUI) that accompanies the S.A.G.E.
 (Statistical Analysis for Genetic Epidemiology) software package.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
System Requirements
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The S.A.G.E.
 programs have been tested to run on Windows XP, Vista and Windows 7.
 The software also runs on Linux 32-bit and 64-bit systems for the Intel
 platform, as well as Linux 64-bit Itanium.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Graphics
