\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
It is always advisable to make sure that the target platform has the most
 current Service Pack and Java version installed.
 The S.A.G.E.
 GUI will not run unless the Java Runtime Environment (JRE) is correctly
 installed on your system.
\end_layout

