\begin_layout Section
Launching S.A.G.E.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Individual S.A.G.E.
 programs may be launched from the command line; however, this manual focuses
 exclusively on use of the GUI to run the programs.
 See the S.A.G.E.
 User Reference Manual for further details on command line options.
 On Windows platforms, double-click the S.A.G.E.
 icon to run the GUI, and on Linux platforms you will need invoke the GUI
 through the standard Java interface.
